          <p>Turn raw data into strategic advantage with custom dashboards, pipelines and predictive models.</p>
          <div class="bento-tags"><span>Power BI</span><span>Python</span><span>ML</span></div>
          <a href="/services/data-analytics" class="bento-link">Explore <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        </div>
