          <div>
            <p class="bento-cta-label">And 8 more services</p>
            <h3 class="bento-cta-heading">Database Architecture · Staff Augmentation · Digital Transformation · LLM Integration · Web & Mobile Apps · QA & Testing · Performance Optimisation · Deployment</h3>
          </div>
          <a href="/services" class="btn-primary bento-cta-btn">
            View All 20 Services
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
